<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="gift-n">gift <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɡɪft/    美 /ɡɪft/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-present">1.★ <strong>礼物 (present)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>a birthday / wedding / Christmas gift</strong>
生日/结婚/圣诞礼物</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>give sb a gift / receive a gift</strong>
送某人礼物/收到礼物</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a <strong>free gift</strong>
赠品</p></div>

<h4 id="2-talent">2.★ <strong>天赋；天资；才能(talent)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a man with many gifts
多才多艺的人</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He has a <strong>gift for</strong> music.
他有音乐天赋。</p></div></div>